description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'ONE DIRECTION 15 MIN DANCE PARTY WORKOUT - Full Body/No Equipment' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: A full body DANCE cardio routine to One Direction classics! A great way to get a sweat on, and it's guaranteed to put a smile on your face! Celebrating 10 years of 1D with some dance Fitness!! Niall Horan, Louis Tomlinson, Harry Styles, Liam Payne, Zayn Malik.
#OneDirection #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout
